plot: POSSESSION is a drama/action film in which two powers form a bond to seek answers on a deal gone bad. They both agree to rid of those who stand in their way and after given what they ask for the body count begin to rise. The intensity and deceit that follows the two bosses from the very beginning which leads them to an epic moment.
